

        %Fb%%Fu%dbslides%RF%

        %fb%Slides file must be named 01 up to 99
        00 is only shown once (this slide)

        %fg%. or >      %fb%next slide
        %fg%, or <      %fb%previous slide

        %fg%r           %fb%reload current slide

        %fg%f           %fb%go to first slide
        %fg%l           %fb%go to last slide

        %fg%gx<enter>   %fb%go to slide x (no leading 0)

        %fg%q           %fb%quit




        %fy%This slide is only shown once

        %Fb%Press 'next slide' to start
    